cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with improving the performance of deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves adding auxiliary supervision branches during training, which is a technique used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also evaluates the performance of the method on classification tasks, which is a common topic in natural language processing (cs.CL).
